1. John Smith – john.smith@example.com
2. Emily Johnson – emily.johnson@creative.com
3. Michael Brown – michael.brown@financepro.com
4. Sarah Davis – sarah.davis@healthware.com

If you need anything else, just let me know.

Best regards,
[Your Name]"}
